Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一個女人那麼早在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你就別在意  過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡花嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,全員…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,給我狠狠地打!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,冰結術!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人跟上那兩個蠢貨!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「驅夜」要來了  請閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和聽說的一樣  好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是白鯨…
